41/* convert 16.16 fixed point to floating point */
42static double conv_fx( int32_t fx ) {
43 double fp = fx;
44 fp /= 65536.;
45 return fp;
46}

48/* some functions for mp4 encoding of variables */
49#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
50static void MP4_ConvertDate2Str( char *psz, uint64_t i_date, bool b_relative )
51{
52 int i_day;
53 int i_hour;
54 int i_min;
55 int i_sec;
56
57 /* date begin at 1 jan 1904 */
58 if ( !b_relative )
59 i_date += ((INT64_C(1904) * 365) + 17) * 24 * 60 * 60;
60
61 i_day = i_date / ( 60*60*24);
62 i_hour = ( i_date /( 60*60 ) ) % 60;
63 i_min = ( i_date / 60 ) % 60;
64 i_sec = i_date % 60;
65 sprintf( psz, "%dd-%2.2dh:%2.2dm:%2.2ds", i_day, i_hour, i_min, i_sec );
66}
67#endif

69/*****************************************************************************
70 * Some prototypes.
71 *****************************************************************************/
72static MP4_Box_t *MP4_ReadBox( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_father );
73
74
75/*****************************************************************************
76 * MP4_ReadBoxCommon : Load only common parameters for all boxes
77 *****************************************************************************
78 * p_box need to be an already allocated MP4_Box_t, and all data
79 * will only be peek not read
80 *
81 * RETURN : 0 if it fail, 1 otherwise
82 *****************************************************************************/
83int MP4_ReadBoxCommon( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
84{
85 int i_read;
86 const uint8_t *p_peek;
87
88 if( ( ( i_read = stream_Peek( p_stream, &p_peek, 32 ) ) < 8 ) )
89 {
90 return 0;
91 }
92 p_box->i_pos = stream_Tell( p_stream );
93
94 p_box->data.p_payload = NULL;
95 p_box->p_father = NULL;
96 p_box->p_first = NULL;
97 p_box->p_last = NULL;
98 p_box->p_next = NULL;
99
100 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->i_shortsize );
101 MP4_GETFOURCC( p_box->i_type );
102
103 /* Now special case */
104
105 if( p_box->i_shortsize == 1 )
106 {
107 /* get the true size on 64 bits */
108 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->i_size );
109 }
110 else
111 {
112 p_box->i_size = p_box->i_shortsize;
113 /* XXX size of 0 means that the box extends to end of file */
114 }
115
116 if( p_box->i_type == ATOM_uuid )
117 {
118 /* get extented type on 16 bytes */
119 GetUUID( &p_box->i_uuid, p_peek );
120 p_peek += 16; i_read -= 16;
121 }
122 else
123 {
124 CreateUUID( &p_box->i_uuid, p_box->i_type );
125 }
126#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
127 if( p_box->i_size )
128 {
129 if MP4_BOX_TYPE_ASCII()
130 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "found Box: %4.4s size %"PRId64" %"PRId64,
131 (char*)&p_box->i_type, p_box->i_size, p_box->i_pos );
132 else
133 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "found Box: c%3.3s size %"PRId64,
134 (char*)&p_box->i_type+1, p_box->i_size );
135 }
136#endif
137
138 return 1;
139}
140
141/*****************************************************************************
142 * MP4_NextBox : Go to the next box
143 *****************************************************************************
144 * if p_box == NULL, go to the next box in which we are( at the begining ).
145 *****************************************************************************/
146static int MP4_NextBox( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
147{
148 MP4_Box_t box;
149
150 if( !p_box )
151 {
152 MP4_ReadBoxCommon( p_stream, &box );
153 p_box = &box;
154 }
155
156 if( !p_box->i_size )
157 {
158 return 2; /* Box with infinite size */
159 }
160
161 if( p_box->p_father )
162 {
163 /* if father's size == 0, it means unknown or infinite size,
164 * and we skip the followong check */
165 if( p_box->p_father->i_size > 0 )
166 {
167 const off_t i_box_end = p_box->i_size + p_box->i_pos;
168 const off_t i_father_end = p_box->p_father->i_size + p_box->p_father->i_pos;
169
170 /* check if it's within p-father */
171 if( i_box_end >= i_father_end )
172 {
173 if( i_box_end > i_father_end )
174 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "out of bound child" );
175 return 0; /* out of bound */
176 }
177 }
178 }
179 if( stream_Seek( p_stream, p_box->i_size + p_box->i_pos ) )
180 {
181 return 0;
182 }
183
184 return 1;
185}
186
187/*****************************************************************************
188 * For all known box a loader is given,
189 * XXX: all common struct have to be already read by MP4_ReadBoxCommon
190 * after called one of theses functions, file position is unknown
191 * you need to call MP4_GotoBox to go where you want
192 *****************************************************************************/
193int MP4_ReadBoxContainerChildren( stream_t *p_stream,
194 MP4_Box_t *p_container, uint32_t i_last_child )
195{
196 MP4_Box_t *p_box;
197
198 /* Size of root container is set to 0 when unknown, for exemple
199 * with a DASH stream. In that case, we skip the following check */
200 if( p_container->i_size
201 && ( stream_Tell( p_stream ) + 8 >
202 (off_t)(p_container->i_pos + p_container->i_size) )
203 )
204 {
205 /* there is no box to load */
206 return 0;
207 }
208
209 do
210 {
211 if( ( p_box = MP4_ReadBox( p_stream, p_container ) ) == NULL ) break;
212
213 /* chain this box with the father and the other at same level */
214 if( !p_container->p_first ) p_container->p_first = p_box;
215 else p_container->p_last->p_next = p_box;
216 p_container->p_last = p_box;
217
218 if( p_box->i_type == i_last_child )
219 {
220 MP4_NextBox( p_stream, p_box );
221 break;
222 }
223
224 } while( MP4_NextBox( p_stream, p_box ) == 1 );
225
226 return 1;
227}
228
229static int MP4_ReadBoxContainerRaw( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_container )
230{
231 return MP4_ReadBoxContainerChildren( p_stream, p_container, 0 );
232}
233
234static int MP4_ReadBoxContainer( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_container )
235{
236 if( p_container->i_size &&
237 ( p_container->i_size <= (size_t)mp4_box_headersize(p_container ) + 8 ) )
238 {
239 /* container is empty, 8 stand for the first header in this box */
240 return 1;
241 }
242
243 /* enter box */
244 stream_Seek( p_stream, p_container->i_pos +
245 mp4_box_headersize( p_container ) );
246
247 return MP4_ReadBoxContainerRaw( p_stream, p_container );
248}

252 /* Up to now do nothing */
253 (void)p_box;

256static int MP4_ReadBoxSkip( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
257{
258 /* XXX sometime moov is hiden in a free box */
259 if( p_box->p_father &&
260 p_box->p_father->i_type == ATOM_root &&
261 p_box->i_type == ATOM_free )
262 {
263 const uint8_t *p_peek;
264 int i_read;
265 vlc_fourcc_t i_fcc;
266
267 i_read = stream_Peek( p_stream, &p_peek, 44 );
268
269 p_peek += mp4_box_headersize( p_box ) + 4;
270 i_read -= mp4_box_headersize( p_box ) + 4;
271
272 if( i_read >= 8 )
273 {
274 i_fcc = VLC_FOURCC( p_peek[0], p_peek[1], p_peek[2], p_peek[3] );
275
276 if( i_fcc == ATOM_cmov || i_fcc == ATOM_mvhd )
277 {
278 msg_Warn( p_stream, "detected moov hidden in a free box ..." );
279
280 p_box->i_type = ATOM_foov;
281 return MP4_ReadBoxContainer( p_stream, p_box );
282 }
283 }
284 }
285
286 /* Nothing to do */
287#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
288 if MP4_BOX_TYPE_ASCII()
289 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "skip box: \"%4.4s\"", (char*)&p_box->i_type );
290 else
291 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "skip box: \"c%3.3s\"", (char*)&p_box->i_type+1 );
292#endif
293 return 1;
294}

296static int MP4_ReadBox_ftyp( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
297{
298 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_ftyp_t );
299
300 MP4_GETFOURCC( p_box->data.p_ftyp->i_major_brand );
301 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_ftyp->i_minor_version );
302
303 if( ( p_box->data.p_ftyp->i_compatible_brands_count = i_read / 4 ) )
304 {
305 uint32_t *tab = p_box->data.p_ftyp->i_compatible_brands =
306 calloc( p_box->data.p_ftyp->i_compatible_brands_count,
307 sizeof(uint32_t));
308
309 if( unlikely( tab == NULL ) )
310 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
311
312 for( unsigned i = 0; i < p_box->data.p_ftyp->i_compatible_brands_count; i++ )
313 {
314 MP4_GETFOURCC( tab[i] );
315 }
316 }
317 else
318 {
319 p_box->data.p_ftyp->i_compatible_brands = NULL;
320 }
321
322 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
323}
324
325static void MP4_FreeBox_ftyp( MP4_Box_t *p_box )
326{
327 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_ftyp->i_compatible_brands );
328}

331static int MP4_ReadBox_mvhd( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
332{
333#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
334 char s_creation_time[128];
335 char s_modification_time[128];
336 char s_duration[128];
337#endif
338 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_mvhd_t );
339
340 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_mvhd );
341
342 if( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_version )
343 {
344 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_creation_time );
345 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_modification_time );
346 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_timescale );
347 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_duration );
348 }
349 else
350 {
351 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_creation_time );
352 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_modification_time );
353 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_timescale );
354 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_duration );
355 }
356 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_rate );
357 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_volume );
358 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_reserved1 );
359
360
361 for( unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++ )
362 {
363 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_reserved2[i] );
364 }
365 for( unsigned i = 0; i < 9; i++ )
366 {
367 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_matrix[i] );
368 }
369 for( unsigned i = 0; i < 6; i++ )
370 {
371 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_predefined[i] );
372 }
373
374 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_next_track_id );
375
376
377#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
378 MP4_ConvertDate2Str( s_creation_time, p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_creation_time, false );
379 MP4_ConvertDate2Str( s_modification_time,
380 p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_modification_time, false );
381 if( p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_rate )
382 {
383 MP4_ConvertDate2Str( s_duration,
384 p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_duration / p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_rate, true );
385 }
386 else
387 {
388 s_duration[0] = 0;
389 }
390 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"mvhd\" creation %s modification %s time scale %d duration %s rate %f volume %f next track id %d",
391 s_creation_time,
392 s_modification_time,
393 (uint32_t)p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_timescale,
394 s_duration,
395 (float)p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_rate / (1<<16 ),
396 (float)p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_volume / 256 ,
397 (uint32_t)p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_next_track_id );
398#endif
399 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
400}

417static int MP4_ReadBox_tfxd( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
418{
419 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_tfxd_t );
420
421 MP4_Box_data_tfxd_t *p_tfxd_data = p_box->data.p_tfxd;
422 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_tfxd_data );
423
424 if( p_tfxd_data->i_version == 0 )
425 {
426 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_tfxd_data->i_fragment_abs_time );
427 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_tfxd_data->i_fragment_duration );
428 }
429 else
430 {
431 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_tfxd_data->i_fragment_abs_time );
432 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_tfxd_data->i_fragment_duration );
433 }
434
435#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
436 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"tfxd\" version %d, flags 0x%x, "\
437 "fragment duration %"PRIu64", fragment abs time %"PRIu64,
438 p_tfxd_data->i_version,
439 p_tfxd_data->i_flags,
440 p_tfxd_data->i_fragment_duration,
441 p_tfxd_data->i_fragment_abs_time
442 );
443#endif
444
445 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
446}

448static int MP4_ReadBox_tfrf( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
449{
450 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_tfxd_t );
451
452 MP4_Box_data_tfrf_t *p_tfrf_data = p_box->data.p_tfrf;
453 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_tfrf_data );
454
455 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_tfrf_data->i_fragment_count );
456
457 p_tfrf_data->p_tfrf_data_fields = calloc( p_tfrf_data->i_fragment_count,
458 sizeof( TfrfBoxDataFields_t ) );
459 if( !p_tfrf_data->p_tfrf_data_fields )
460 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
461
462 for( uint8_t i = 0; i < p_tfrf_data->i_fragment_count; i++ )
463 {
464 TfrfBoxDataFields_t *TfrfBoxDataField = &p_tfrf_data->p_tfrf_data_fields[i];
465 if( p_tfrf_data->i_version == 0 )
466 {
467 MP4_GET4BYTES( TfrfBoxDataField->i_fragment_abs_time );
468 MP4_GET4BYTES( TfrfBoxDataField->i_fragment_duration );
469 }
470 else
471 {
472 MP4_GET8BYTES( TfrfBoxDataField->i_fragment_abs_time );
473 MP4_GET8BYTES( TfrfBoxDataField->i_fragment_duration );
474 }
475 }
476
477#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
478 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"tfrf\" version %d, flags 0x%x, "\
479 "fragment count %"PRIu8, p_tfrf_data->i_version,
480 p_tfrf_data->i_flags, p_tfrf_data->i_fragment_count );
481
482 for( uint8_t i = 0; i < p_tfrf_data->i_fragment_count; i++ )
483 {
484 TfrfBoxDataFields_t *TfrfBoxDataField = &p_tfrf_data->p_tfrf_data_fields[i];
485 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "\"tfrf\" fragment duration %"PRIu64", "\
486 "fragment abs time %"PRIu64,
487 TfrfBoxDataField->i_fragment_duration,
488 TfrfBoxDataField->i_fragment_abs_time );
489 }
490
491#endif
492
493 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
494}

496static void MP4_FreeBox_tfrf( MP4_Box_t *p_box )
497{
498 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_tfrf->p_tfrf_data_fields );
499}

501static int MP4_ReadBox_stra( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
502{
503 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_stra_t );
504 MP4_Box_data_stra_t *p_stra = p_box->data.p_stra;
505
506 uint8_t i_reserved;
507 VLC_UNUSED(i_reserved);
508 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_stra->i_es_cat );
509 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_reserved );
510 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_stra->i_track_ID );
511
512 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_stra->i_timescale );
513 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_stra->i_duration );
514
515 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_stra->FourCC );
516 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_stra->Bitrate );
517 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_stra->MaxWidth );
518 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_stra->MaxHeight );
519 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_stra->SamplingRate );
520 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_stra->Channels );
521 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_stra->BitsPerSample );
522 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_stra->AudioTag );
523 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_stra->nBlockAlign );
524
525 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_reserved );
526 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_reserved );
527 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_reserved );
528 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_stra->cpd_len );
529 if( p_stra->cpd_len > i_read )
530 goto error;
531 p_stra->CodecPrivateData = malloc( p_stra->cpd_len );
532 if( unlikely( p_stra->CodecPrivateData == NULL ) )
533 goto error;
534 memcpy( p_stra->CodecPrivateData, p_peek, p_stra->cpd_len );
535
536#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
537 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "es_cat is %"PRIu8", birate is %"PRIu32,
538 p_stra->i_es_cat, p_stra->Bitrate );
539#endif
540
541 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
542error:
543 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
544}

546static void MP4_FreeBox_stra( MP4_Box_t *p_box )
547{
548 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_stra->CodecPrivateData );
549}

551static int MP4_ReadBox_uuid( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
552{
553 if( !CmpUUID( &p_box->i_uuid, &TfrfBoxUUID ) )
554 return MP4_ReadBox_tfrf( p_stream, p_box );
555 if( !CmpUUID( &p_box->i_uuid, &TfxdBoxUUID ) )
556 return MP4_ReadBox_tfxd( p_stream, p_box );
557 if( !CmpUUID( &p_box->i_uuid, &SmooBoxUUID ) )
558 return MP4_ReadBoxContainer( p_stream, p_box );
559 if( !CmpUUID( &p_box->i_uuid, &StraBoxUUID ) )
560 return MP4_ReadBox_stra( p_stream, p_box );
561
562 msg_Warn( p_stream, "Unknown uuid type box" );
563 return 1;
564}
565
566static void MP4_FreeBox_uuid( MP4_Box_t *p_box )
567{
568 if( !CmpUUID( &p_box->i_uuid, &TfrfBoxUUID ) )
569 return MP4_FreeBox_tfrf( p_box );
570 if( !CmpUUID( &p_box->i_uuid, &TfxdBoxUUID ) )
571 return MP4_FreeBox_Common( p_box );
572 if( !CmpUUID( &p_box->i_uuid, &SmooBoxUUID ) )
573 return MP4_FreeBox_Common( p_box );
574 if( !CmpUUID( &p_box->i_uuid, &StraBoxUUID ) )
575 return MP4_FreeBox_stra( p_box );
576}

578static int MP4_ReadBox_sidx( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
579{
580 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_sidx_t );
581
582 MP4_Box_data_sidx_t *p_sidx_data = p_box->data.p_sidx;
583 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_sidx_data );
584
585 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_sidx_data->i_reference_ID );
586 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_sidx_data->i_timescale );
587
588 if( p_sidx_data->i_version == 0 )
589 {
590 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_sidx_data->i_earliest_presentation_time );
591 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_sidx_data->i_first_offset );
592 }
593 else
594 {
595 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_sidx_data->i_earliest_presentation_time );
596 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_sidx_data->i_first_offset );
597 }
598
599 uint16_t i_reserved;
600 VLC_UNUSED(i_reserved);
601 MP4_GET2BYTES( i_reserved );
602 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_sidx_data->i_reference_count );
603 uint16_t i_count = p_sidx_data->i_reference_count;
604
605 p_sidx_data->p_items = calloc( i_count, sizeof( MP4_Box_sidx_item_t ) );
606 uint32_t tmp;
607 for( unsigned i = 0; i < i_count; i++ )
608 {
609 MP4_GET4BYTES( tmp );
610 p_sidx_data->p_items[i].b_reference_type = (bool)((tmp & 0x80000000)>>24);
611 p_sidx_data->p_items[i].i_referenced_size = tmp & 0x7fffffff;
612 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_sidx_data->p_items[i].i_subsegment_duration );
613
614 MP4_GET4BYTES( tmp );
615 p_sidx_data->p_items[i].b_starts_with_SAP = (bool)((tmp & 0x80000000)>>24);
616 p_sidx_data->p_items[i].i_SAP_type = (tmp & 0x70000000)>>24;
617 p_sidx_data->p_items[i].i_SAP_delta_time = tmp & 0xfffffff;
618 }
619
620#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
621 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"sidx\" version %d, flags 0x%x, "\
622 "ref_ID %"PRIu32", timescale %"PRIu32", ref_count %"PRIu16", "\
623 "first subsegmt duration %"PRIu32,
624 p_sidx_data->i_version,
625 p_sidx_data->i_flags,
626 p_sidx_data->i_reference_ID,
627 p_sidx_data->i_timescale,
628 p_sidx_data->i_reference_count,
629 p_sidx_data->p_items[0].i_subsegment_duration
630 );
631#endif
632
633 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
634}

636static void MP4_FreeBox_sidx( MP4_Box_t *p_box )
637{
638 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_sidx->p_items );
639}

641static int MP4_ReadBox_tfhd( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
642{
643 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_tfhd_t );
644
645 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_tfhd );
646
647 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_version != 0 )
648 {
649 msg_Warn( p_stream, "'tfhd' box with version != 0. "\
650 " Don't know what to do with that, please patch" );
651 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
652 }
653
654 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_track_ID );
655
656 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_DURATION_IS_EMPTY )
657 {
658 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "'duration-is-empty' flag is present "\
659 "=> no samples for this time interval." );
660 p_box->data.p_tfhd->b_empty = true;
661 }
662 else
663 p_box->data.p_tfhd->b_empty = false;
664
665 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_BASE_DATA_OFFSET )
666 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_base_data_offset );
667 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_SAMPLE_DESC_INDEX )
668 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_sample_description_index );
669 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_DFLT_SAMPLE_DURATION )
670 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_default_sample_duration );
671 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_DFLT_SAMPLE_SIZE )
672 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_default_sample_size );
673 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_DFLT_SAMPLE_FLAGS )
674 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_default_sample_flags );
675
676#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
677 char psz_base[128] = "\0";
678 char psz_desc[128] = "\0";
679 char psz_dura[128] = "\0";
680 char psz_size[128] = "\0";
681 char psz_flag[128] = "\0";
682 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_BASE_DATA_OFFSET )
683 snprintf(psz_base, sizeof(psz_base), "base offset %"PRId64, p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_base_data_offset);
684 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_SAMPLE_DESC_INDEX )
685 snprintf(psz_desc, sizeof(psz_desc), "sample description index %d", p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_sample_description_index);
686 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_DFLT_SAMPLE_DURATION )
687 snprintf(psz_dura, sizeof(psz_dura), "sample duration %d", p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_default_sample_duration);
688 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_DFLT_SAMPLE_SIZE )
689 snprintf(psz_size, sizeof(psz_size), "sample size %d", p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_default_sample_size);
690 if( p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags & MP4_TFHD_DFLT_SAMPLE_FLAGS )
691 snprintf(psz_flag, sizeof(psz_flag), "sample flags 0x%x", p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_default_sample_flags);
692
693 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"tfhd\" version %d flags 0x%x track ID %d %s %s %s %s %s",
694 p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_version,
695 p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_flags,
696 p_box->data.p_tfhd->i_track_ID,
697 psz_base, psz_desc, psz_dura, psz_size, psz_flag );
698#endif
699
700 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
701}

703static int MP4_ReadBox_trun( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
704{
705 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_trun_t );
706
707 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_trun );
708
709 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_trun->i_sample_count );
710
711 if( p_box->data.p_trun->i_flags & MP4_TRUN_DATA_OFFSET )
712 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_trun->i_data_offset );
713 if( p_box->data.p_trun->i_flags & MP4_TRUN_FIRST_FLAGS )
714 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_trun->i_first_sample_flags );
715
716 p_box->data.p_trun->p_samples =
717 calloc( p_box->data.p_trun->i_sample_count, sizeof(MP4_descriptor_trun_sample_t) );
718 if ( p_box->data.p_trun->p_samples == NULL )
719 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
720
721 for( unsigned int i = 0; i<p_box->data.p_trun->i_sample_count; i++ )
722 {
723 MP4_descriptor_trun_sample_t *p_sample = &p_box->data.p_trun->p_samples[i];
724 if( p_box->data.p_trun->i_flags & MP4_TRUN_SAMPLE_DURATION )
725 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_sample->i_duration );
726 if( p_box->data.p_trun->i_flags & MP4_TRUN_SAMPLE_SIZE )
727 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_sample->i_size );
728 if( p_box->data.p_trun->i_flags & MP4_TRUN_SAMPLE_FLAGS )
729 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_sample->i_flags );
730 if( p_box->data.p_trun->i_flags & MP4_TRUN_SAMPLE_TIME_OFFSET )
731 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_sample->i_composition_time_offset );
732 }
733
734#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
735 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"trun\" version %u flags 0x%x sample count %u",
736 p_box->data.p_trun->i_version,
737 p_box->data.p_trun->i_flags,
738 p_box->data.p_trun->i_sample_count );
739
740 for( unsigned int i = 0; i<p_box->data.p_trun->i_sample_count; i++ )
741 {
742 MP4_descriptor_trun_sample_t *p_sample = &p_box->data.p_trun->p_samples[i];
743 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"trun\" sample %4.4u flags 0x%x "\
744 "duration %"PRIu32" size %"PRIu32" composition time offset %"PRIu32,
745 i, p_sample->i_flags, p_sample->i_duration,
746 p_sample->i_size, p_sample->i_composition_time_offset );
747 }
748#endif
749
750 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
751}

753static void MP4_FreeBox_trun( MP4_Box_t *p_box )
754{
755 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_trun->p_samples );
756}

758
759static int MP4_ReadBox_tkhd( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
760{
761#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
762 char s_creation_time[128];
763 char s_modification_time[128];
764 char s_duration[128];
765#endif
766 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_tkhd_t );
767
768 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_tkhd );
769
770 if( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_version )
771 {
772 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_creation_time );
773 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_modification_time );
774 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_track_ID );
775 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_reserved );
776 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_duration );
777 }
778 else
779 {
780 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_creation_time );
781 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_modification_time );
782 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_track_ID );
783 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_reserved );
784 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_duration );
785 }
786
787 for( unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++ )
788 {
789 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_reserved2[i] );
790 }
791 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_layer );
792 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_predefined );
793 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_volume );
794 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_reserved3 );
795
796 for( unsigned i = 0; i < 9; i++ )
797 {
798 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix[i] );
799 }
800 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_width );
801 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_height );
802
803 double rotation; //angle in degrees to be rotated clockwise
804 double scale[2]; // scale factor; sx = scale[0] , sy = scale[1]
805 double translate[2];// amount to translate; tx = translate[0] , ty = translate[1]
806
807 int32_t *matrix = p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix;
808
809 translate[0] = conv_fx(matrix[6]);
810 translate[1] = conv_fx(matrix[7]);
811
812 scale[0] = sqrt(conv_fx(matrix[0]) * conv_fx(matrix[0]) +
813 conv_fx(matrix[3]) * conv_fx(matrix[3]));
814 scale[1] = sqrt(conv_fx(matrix[1]) * conv_fx(matrix[1]) +
815 conv_fx(matrix[4]) * conv_fx(matrix[4]));
816
817 rotation = atan2(conv_fx(matrix[1]) / scale[1], conv_fx(matrix[0]) / scale[0]) * 180 / M_PI;
818
819 if (rotation < 0)
820 rotation += 360.;
821
822 p_box->data.p_tkhd->f_rotation = rotation;
823
824#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
825 MP4_ConvertDate2Str( s_creation_time, p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_creation_time, false );
826 MP4_ConvertDate2Str( s_modification_time, p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_modification_time, false );
827 MP4_ConvertDate2Str( s_duration, p_box->data.p_mvhd->i_duration, true );
828
829 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"tkhd\" creation %s modification %s duration %s track ID %d layer %d volume %f rotation %f scaleX %f scaleY %f translateX %f translateY %f width %f height %f. "
830 "Matrix: %i %i %i %i %i %i %i %i %i",
831 s_creation_time,
832 s_modification_time,
833 s_duration,
834 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_track_ID,
835 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_layer,
836 (float)p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_volume / 256 ,
837 rotation,
838 scale[0],
839 scale[1],
840 translate[0],
841 translate[1],
842 (float)p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_width / BLOCK16x16,
843 (float)p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_height / BLOCK16x16,
844 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix[0],
845 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix[1],
846 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix[2],
847 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix[3],
848 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix[4],
849 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix[5],
850 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix[6],
851 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix[7],
852 p_box->data.p_tkhd->i_matrix[8] );
853#endif
854 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
855}

858static int MP4_ReadBox_mdhd( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
859{
860 uint16_t i_language;
861#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
862 char s_creation_time[128];
863 char s_modification_time[128];
864 char s_duration[128];
865#endif
866 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_mdhd_t );
867
868 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_mdhd );
869
870 if( p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_version )
871 {
872 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_creation_time );
873 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_modification_time );
874 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_timescale );
875 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_duration );
876 }
877 else
878 {
879 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_creation_time );
880 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_modification_time );
881 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_timescale );
882 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_duration );
883 }
884 p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_language_code = i_language = GetWBE( p_peek );
885 for( unsigned i = 0; i < 3; i++ )
886 {
887 p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_language[i] =
888 ( ( i_language >> ( (2-i)*5 ) )&0x1f ) + 0x60;
889 }
890
891 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_predefined );
892
893#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
894 MP4_ConvertDate2Str( s_creation_time, p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_creation_time, false );
895 MP4_ConvertDate2Str( s_modification_time, p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_modification_time, false );
896 MP4_ConvertDate2Str( s_duration, p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_duration, true );
897 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"mdhd\" creation %s modification %s time scale %d duration %s language %c%c%c",
898 s_creation_time,
899 s_modification_time,
900 (uint32_t)p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_timescale,
901 s_duration,
902 p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_language[0],
903 p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_language[1],
904 p_box->data.p_mdhd->i_language[2] );
905#endif
906 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
907}

910static int MP4_ReadBox_hdlr( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
911{
912 int32_t i_reserved;
913 VLC_UNUSED(i_reserved);
914
915 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_hdlr_t );
916
917 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_hdlr );
918
919 MP4_GETFOURCC( p_box->data.p_hdlr->i_predefined );
920 MP4_GETFOURCC( p_box->data.p_hdlr->i_handler_type );
921
922 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_reserved );
923 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_reserved );
924 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_reserved );
925 p_box->data.p_hdlr->psz_name = NULL;
926
927 if( i_read > 0 )
928 {
929 uint8_t *psz = p_box->data.p_hdlr->psz_name = malloc( i_read + 1 );
930 if( unlikely( psz == NULL ) )
931 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
932
933 /* Yes, I love .mp4 :( */
934 if( p_box->data.p_hdlr->i_predefined == VLC_FOURCC( 'm', 'h', 'l', 'r' ) )
935 {
936 uint8_t i_len;
937 int i_copy;
938
939 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_len );
940 i_copy = __MIN( i_read, i_len );
941
942 memcpy( psz, p_peek, i_copy );
943 p_box->data.p_hdlr->psz_name[i_copy] = '\0';
944 }
945 else
946 {
947 memcpy( psz, p_peek, i_read );
948 p_box->data.p_hdlr->psz_name[i_read] = '\0';
949 }
950 }
951
952#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
953 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"hdlr\" handler type: \"%4.4s\" name: \"%s\"",
954 (char*)&p_box->data.p_hdlr->i_handler_type,
955 p_box->data.p_hdlr->psz_name );
956
957#endif
958 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
959}

1108 p_box->data.p_stts->pi_sample_count =
1109 calloc( p_box->data.p_stts->i_entry_count, sizeof(uint32_t) );
1110 p_box->data.p_stts->pi_sample_delta =
1111 calloc( p_box->data.p_stts->i_entry_count, sizeof(int32_t) );
1112 if( p_box->data.p_stts->pi_sample_count == NULL
1113 || p_box->data.p_stts->pi_sample_delta == NULL )
1114 {
1115 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
1116 }
1117
1118 uint32_t i = 0;
1119 for( ; (i < p_box->data.p_stts->i_entry_count )&&( i_read >=8 ); i++ )
1120 {
1121 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_stts->pi_sample_count[i] );
1122 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_stts->pi_sample_delta[i] );
1123 }
1124
1125 if ( i < p_box->data.p_stts->i_entry_count )
1126 p_box->data.p_stts->i_entry_count = i;
1127
1128#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1129 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"stts\" entry-count %d",
1130 p_box->data.p_stts->i_entry_count );
1131
1132#endif
1133 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
1134}

1178
1179static int MP4_ReadLengthDescriptor( uint8_t **pp_peek, int64_t *i_read )
1180{
1181 unsigned int i_b;
1182 unsigned int i_len = 0;
1183 do
1184 {
1185 i_b = **pp_peek;
1186
1187 (*pp_peek)++;
1188 (*i_read)--;
1189 i_len = ( i_len << 7 ) + ( i_b&0x7f );
1190 } while( i_b&0x80 );
1191 return( i_len );
1192}

1195static void MP4_FreeBox_esds( MP4_Box_t *p_box )
1196{
1197 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_esds->es_descriptor.psz_URL );
1198 if( p_box->data.p_esds->es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr )
1199 {
1200 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_esds->es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->p_decoder_specific_info );
1201 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_esds->es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr );
1202 }
1203}
1204
1205static int MP4_ReadBox_esds( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
1206{
1207#define es_descriptor p_box->data.p_esds->es_descriptor
1208 unsigned int i_len;
1209 unsigned int i_flags;
1210 unsigned int i_type;
1211
1212 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_esds_t );
1213
1214 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_esds );
1215
1216
1217 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_type );
1218 if( i_type == 0x03 ) /* MP4ESDescrTag */
1219 {
1220 i_len = MP4_ReadLengthDescriptor( &p_peek, &i_read );
1221
1222#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1223 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "found esds MPEG4ESDescr (%dBytes)",
1224 i_len );
1225#endif
1226
1227 MP4_GET2BYTES( es_descriptor.i_ES_ID );
1228 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_flags );
1229 es_descriptor.b_stream_dependence = ( (i_flags&0x80) != 0);
1230 es_descriptor.b_url = ( (i_flags&0x40) != 0);
1231 es_descriptor.b_OCRstream = ( (i_flags&0x20) != 0);
1232
1233 es_descriptor.i_stream_priority = i_flags&0x1f;
1234 if( es_descriptor.b_stream_dependence )
1235 {
1236 MP4_GET2BYTES( es_descriptor.i_depend_on_ES_ID );
1237 }
1238 if( es_descriptor.b_url )
1239 {
1240 unsigned int i_len;
1241
1242 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_len );
1243 es_descriptor.psz_URL = malloc( i_len + 1 );
1244 if( es_descriptor.psz_URL )
1245 {
1246 memcpy( es_descriptor.psz_URL, p_peek, i_len );
1247 es_descriptor.psz_URL[i_len] = 0;
1248 }
1249 p_peek += i_len;
1250 i_read -= i_len;
1251 }
1252 else
1253 {
1254 es_descriptor.psz_URL = NULL;
1255 }
1256 if( es_descriptor.b_OCRstream )
1257 {
1258 MP4_GET2BYTES( es_descriptor.i_OCR_ES_ID );
1259 }
1260 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_type ); /* get next type */
1261 }
1262
1263 if( i_type != 0x04)/* MP4DecConfigDescrTag */
1264 {
1265 es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr = NULL;
1266 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 ); /* rest isn't interesting up to now */
1267 }
1268
1269 i_len = MP4_ReadLengthDescriptor( &p_peek, &i_read );
1270
1271#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1272 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "found esds MP4DecConfigDescr (%dBytes)",
1273 i_len );
1274#endif
1275
1276 es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr =
1277 calloc( 1, sizeof( MP4_descriptor_decoder_config_t ));
1278 if( unlikely( es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr == NULL ) )
1279 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
1280
1281 MP4_GET1BYTE( es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->i_objectTypeIndication );
1282 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_flags );
1283 es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->i_streamType = i_flags >> 2;
1284 es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->b_upStream = ( i_flags >> 1 )&0x01;
1285 MP4_GET3BYTES( es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->i_buffer_sizeDB );
1286 MP4_GET4BYTES( es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->i_max_bitrate );
1287 MP4_GET4BYTES( es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->i_avg_bitrate );
1288 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_type );
1289 if( i_type != 0x05 )/* MP4DecSpecificDescrTag */
1290 {
1291 es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->i_decoder_specific_info_len = 0;
1292 es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->p_decoder_specific_info = NULL;
1293 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
1294 }
1295
1296 i_len = MP4_ReadLengthDescriptor( &p_peek, &i_read );
1297
1298#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1299 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "found esds MP4DecSpecificDescr (%dBytes)",
1300 i_len );
1301#endif
1302 if( i_len > i_read )
1303 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
1304
1305 es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->i_decoder_specific_info_len = i_len;
1306 es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->p_decoder_specific_info = malloc( i_len );
1307 if( unlikely( es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->p_decoder_specific_info == NULL ) )
1308 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
1309
1310 memcpy( es_descriptor.p_decConfigDescr->p_decoder_specific_info,
1311 p_peek, i_len );
1312
1313 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
1314#undef es_descriptor
1315}

1343 int i;
1344

1346
1347 if( p_avcC->sps )
1348 {
1349 for( i = 0; i < p_avcC->i_sps; i++ )
1350 FREENULL( p_avcC->sps[i] );
1351 }
1352 if( p_avcC->pps )
1353 {
1354 for( i = 0; i < p_avcC->i_pps; i++ )
1355 FREENULL( p_avcC->pps[i] );
1356 }
1357 if( p_avcC->i_sps > 0 ) FREENULL( p_avcC->sps );
1358 if( p_avcC->i_sps > 0 ) FREENULL( p_avcC->i_sps_length );
1359 if( p_avcC->i_pps > 0 ) FREENULL( p_avcC->pps );
1360 if( p_avcC->i_pps > 0 ) FREENULL( p_avcC->i_pps_length );

1362
1363static int MP4_ReadBox_avcC( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
1364{
1365 MP4_Box_data_avcC_t *p_avcC;
1366 int i;
1367
1368 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_avcC_t );
1369 p_avcC = p_box->data.p_avcC;
1370
1371 p_avcC->i_avcC = i_read;
1372 if( p_avcC->i_avcC > 0 )
1373 {
1374 uint8_t * p = p_avcC->p_avcC = malloc( p_avcC->i_avcC );
1375 if( p )
1376 memcpy( p, p_peek, i_read );
1377 }
1378
1379 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_avcC->i_version );
1380 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_avcC->i_profile );
1381 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_avcC->i_profile_compatibility );
1382 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_avcC->i_level );
1383 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_avcC->i_reserved1 );
1384 p_avcC->i_length_size = (p_avcC->i_reserved1&0x03) + 1;
1385 p_avcC->i_reserved1 >>= 2;
1386
1387 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_avcC->i_reserved2 );
1388 p_avcC->i_sps = p_avcC->i_reserved2&0x1f;
1389 p_avcC->i_reserved2 >>= 5;
1390
1391 if( p_avcC->i_sps > 0 )
1392 {
1393 p_avcC->i_sps_length = calloc( p_avcC->i_sps, sizeof( uint16_t ) );
1394 p_avcC->sps = calloc( p_avcC->i_sps, sizeof( uint8_t* ) );
1395
1396 if( !p_avcC->i_sps_length || !p_avcC->sps )
1397 goto error;
1398
1399 for( i = 0; i < p_avcC->i_sps; i++ )
1400 {
1401 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_avcC->i_sps_length[i] );
1402 p_avcC->sps[i] = malloc( p_avcC->i_sps_length[i] );
1403 if( p_avcC->sps[i] )
1404 memcpy( p_avcC->sps[i], p_peek, p_avcC->i_sps_length[i] );
1405
1406 p_peek += p_avcC->i_sps_length[i];
1407 i_read -= p_avcC->i_sps_length[i];
1408 }
1409 }
1410
1411 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_avcC->i_pps );
1412 if( p_avcC->i_pps > 0 )
1413 {
1414 p_avcC->i_pps_length = calloc( p_avcC->i_pps, sizeof( uint16_t ) );
1415 p_avcC->pps = calloc( p_avcC->i_pps, sizeof( uint8_t* ) );
1416
1417 if( !p_avcC->i_pps_length || !p_avcC->pps )
1418 goto error;
1419
1420 for( i = 0; i < p_avcC->i_pps; i++ )
1421 {
1422 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_avcC->i_pps_length[i] );
1423 p_avcC->pps[i] = malloc( p_avcC->i_pps_length[i] );
1424 if( p_avcC->pps[i] )
1425 memcpy( p_avcC->pps[i], p_peek, p_avcC->i_pps_length[i] );
1426
1427 p_peek += p_avcC->i_pps_length[i];
1428 i_read -= p_avcC->i_pps_length[i];
1429 }
1430 }
1431#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1432 msg_Dbg( p_stream,
1433 "read box: \"avcC\" version=%d profile=0x%x level=0x%x length size=%d sps=%d pps=%d",
1434 p_avcC->i_version, p_avcC->i_profile, p_avcC->i_level,
1435 p_avcC->i_length_size,
1436 p_avcC->i_sps, p_avcC->i_pps );
1437 for( i = 0; i < p_avcC->i_sps; i++ )
1438 {
1439 msg_Dbg( p_stream, " - sps[%d] length=%d",
1440 i, p_avcC->i_sps_length[i] );
1441 }
1442 for( i = 0; i < p_avcC->i_pps; i++ )
1443 {
1444 msg_Dbg( p_stream, " - pps[%d] length=%d",
1445 i, p_avcC->i_pps_length[i] );
1446 }
1447
1448#endif
1449 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
1450
1451error:
1452 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
1453}

1455static int MP4_ReadBox_dac3( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
1456{
1457 MP4_Box_data_dac3_t *p_dac3;
1458 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_dac3_t );
1459
1460 p_dac3 = p_box->data.p_dac3;
1461
1462 unsigned i_header;
1463 MP4_GET3BYTES( i_header );
1464
1465 p_dac3->i_fscod = ( i_header >> 22 ) & 0x03;
1466 p_dac3->i_bsid = ( i_header >> 17 ) & 0x01f;
1467 p_dac3->i_bsmod = ( i_header >> 14 ) & 0x07;
1468 p_dac3->i_acmod = ( i_header >> 11 ) & 0x07;
1469 p_dac3->i_lfeon = ( i_header >> 10 ) & 0x01;
1470 p_dac3->i_bitrate_code = ( i_header >> 5) & 0x1f;
1471
1472#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1473 msg_Dbg( p_stream,
1474 "read box: \"dac3\" fscod=0x%x bsid=0x%x bsmod=0x%x acmod=0x%x lfeon=0x%x bitrate_code=0x%x",
1475 p_dac3->i_fscod, p_dac3->i_bsid, p_dac3->i_bsmod, p_dac3->i_acmod, p_dac3->i_lfeon, p_dac3->i_bitrate_code );
1476#endif
1477 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
1478}

1480static int MP4_ReadBox_dvc1( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
1481{
1482 MP4_Box_data_dvc1_t *p_dvc1;

1485 p_dvc1 = p_box->data.p_dvc1;

1488 uint8_t i_profile = (p_dvc1->i_profile_level & 0xf0) >> 4;
1489 if( i_profile != 0x06 && i_profile != 0x0c )
1490 {

1492 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );

1496 p_dvc1->i_vc1 = p_box->i_size - 7; /* Header + profile_level */
1497
1498 if( p_dvc1->i_vc1 > 0 )
1499 {
1500 uint8_t *p = p_dvc1->p_vc1 = malloc( p_dvc1->i_vc1 );
1501 if( p )
1502 memcpy( p, p_peek, i_read );
1503 }
1504
1505#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1506 msg_Dbg( p_stream,
1507 "read box: \"dvc1\" profile=%"PRIu8" level=%i",
1508 i_profile, p_dvc1->i_profile_level & 0x0e >> 1 );
1509#endif
1510
1511 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
1512}

1598static int MP4_ReadBox_sample_soun( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
1599{
1600 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_sample_soun_t );
1601 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->p_qt_description = NULL;
1602
1603 /* Sanity check needed because the "wave" box does also contain an
1604 * "mp4a" box that we don't understand. */
1605 if( i_read < 28 )
1606 {
1607 i_read -= 30;
1608 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
1609 }
1610
1611 for( unsigned i = 0; i < 6 ; i++ )
1612 {
1613 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_reserved1[i] );
1614 }
1615
1616 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_data_reference_index );
1617
1618 /*
1619 * XXX hack -> produce a copy of the nearly complete chunk
1620 */
1621 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_qt_description = 0;
1622 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->p_qt_description = NULL;
1623 if( i_read > 0 )
1624 {
1625 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->p_qt_description = malloc( i_read );
1626 if( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->p_qt_description )
1627 {
1628 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_qt_description = i_read;
1629 memcpy( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->p_qt_description, p_peek, i_read );
1630 }
1631 }
1632
1633 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_qt_version );
1634 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_qt_revision_level );
1635 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_qt_vendor );
1636
1637 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_channelcount );
1638 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_samplesize );
1639 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_compressionid );
1640 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_reserved3 );
1641 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sampleratehi );
1642 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sampleratelo );
1643
1644 if( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_qt_version == 1 && i_read >= 16 )
1645 {
1646 /* SoundDescriptionV1 */
1647 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sample_per_packet );
1648 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_bytes_per_packet );
1649 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_bytes_per_frame );
1650 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_bytes_per_sample );
1651
1652#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1653 msg_Dbg( p_stream,
1654 "read box: \"soun\" qt3+ sample/packet=%d bytes/packet=%d "
1655 "bytes/frame=%d bytes/sample=%d",
1656 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sample_per_packet,
1657 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_bytes_per_packet,
1658 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_bytes_per_frame,
1659 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_bytes_per_sample );
1660#endif
1661 stream_Seek( p_stream, p_box->i_pos +
1662 mp4_box_headersize( p_box ) + 44 );
1663 }
1664 else if( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_qt_version == 2 && i_read >= 36 )
1665 {
1666 /* SoundDescriptionV2 */
1667 double f_sample_rate;
1668 int64_t i_dummy64;
1669 uint32_t i_channel, i_extoffset, i_dummy32;
1670
1671 /* Checks */
1672 if ( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_channelcount != 0x3 ||
1673 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_samplesize != 0x0010 ||
1674 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_compressionid != 0xFFFE ||
1675 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_reserved3 != 0x0 ||
1676 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sampleratehi != 0x1 ||//65536
1677 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sampleratelo != 0x0 ) //remainder
1678 {
1679 msg_Err( p_stream, "invalid stsd V2 box defaults" );
1680 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
1681 }
1682 /* !Checks */
1683
1684 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_extoffset ); /* offset to stsd extentions */
1685 MP4_GET8BYTES( i_dummy64 );
1686 memcpy( &f_sample_rate, &i_dummy64, 8 );
1687 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: %f Hz", f_sample_rate );
1688 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sampleratehi = (int)f_sample_rate % BLOCK16x16;
1689 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sampleratelo = f_sample_rate / BLOCK16x16;
1690
1691 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_channel );
1692 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_channelcount = i_channel;
1693
1694 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_dummy32 );
1695 if ( i_dummy32 != 0x7F000000 )
1696 {
1697 msg_Err( p_stream, "invalid stsd V2 box" );
1698 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
1699 }
1700
1701 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_constbitsperchannel );
1702 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_formatflags );
1703 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_constbytesperaudiopacket );
1704 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_constLPCMframesperaudiopacket );
1705
1706#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1707 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"soun\" V2 rate=%f bitsperchannel=%u "
1708 "flags=%u bytesperpacket=%u lpcmframesperpacket=%u",
1709 f_sample_rate,
1710 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_constbitsperchannel,
1711 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_formatflags,
1712 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_constbytesperaudiopacket,
1713 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_constLPCMframesperaudiopacket );
1714#endif
1715 if ( i_extoffset < p_box->i_size )
1716 stream_Seek( p_stream, p_box->i_pos + i_extoffset );
1717 else
1718 stream_Seek( p_stream, p_box->i_pos + p_box->i_size );
1719 }
1720 else
1721 {
1722 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sample_per_packet = 0;
1723 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_bytes_per_packet = 0;
1724 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_bytes_per_frame = 0;
1725 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_bytes_per_sample = 0;
1726
1727#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1728 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"soun\" mp4 or qt1/2 (rest=%"PRId64")",
1729 i_read );
1730#endif
1731 stream_Seek( p_stream, p_box->i_pos +
1732 mp4_box_headersize( p_box ) + 28 );
1733 }
1734
1735 if( p_box->i_type == ATOM_drms )
1736 {
1737 msg_Warn( p_stream, "DRM protected streams are not supported." );
1738 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
1739 }
1740
1741 if( p_box->i_type == ATOM_samr || p_box->i_type == ATOM_sawb )
1742 {
1743 /* Ignore channelcount for AMR (3gpp AMRSpecificBox) */
1744 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_channelcount = 1;
1745 }
1746
1747 /* Loads extensions */
1748 MP4_ReadBoxContainerRaw( p_stream, p_box ); /* esds/wave/... */
1749
1750#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1751 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"soun\" in stsd channel %d "
1752 "sample size %d sample rate %f",
1753 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_channelcount,
1754 p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_samplesize,
1755 (float)p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sampleratehi +
1756 (float)p_box->data.p_sample_soun->i_sampleratelo / BLOCK16x16 );
1757
1758#endif
1759 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
1760}

1764{
1765 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_sample_soun->p_qt_description );
1766}

1769int MP4_ReadBox_sample_vide( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
1770{
1771 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_sample_vide_t );
1772
1773 for( unsigned i = 0; i < 6 ; i++ )
1774 {
1775 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_reserved1[i] );
1776 }
1777
1778 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_data_reference_index );
1779
1780 /*
1781 * XXX hack -> produce a copy of the nearly complete chunk
1782 */
1783 if( i_read > 0 )
1784 {
1785 p_box->data.p_sample_vide->p_qt_image_description = malloc( i_read );
1786 if( unlikely( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->p_qt_image_description == NULL ) )
1787 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
1788 p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_qt_image_description = i_read;
1789 memcpy( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->p_qt_image_description,
1790 p_peek, i_read );
1791 }
1792 else
1793 {
1794 p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_qt_image_description = 0;
1795 p_box->data.p_sample_vide->p_qt_image_description = NULL;
1796 }
1797
1798 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_qt_version );
1799 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_qt_revision_level );
1800 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_qt_vendor );
1801
1802 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_qt_temporal_quality );
1803 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_qt_spatial_quality );
1804
1805 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_width );
1806 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_height );
1807
1808 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_horizresolution );
1809 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_vertresolution );
1810
1811 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_qt_data_size );
1812 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_qt_frame_count );
1813
1814 memcpy( &p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_compressorname, p_peek, 32 );
1815 p_peek += 32; i_read -= 32;
1816
1817 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_depth );
1818 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_qt_color_table );
1819
1820 stream_Seek( p_stream, p_box->i_pos + mp4_box_headersize( p_box ) + 78);
1821
1822 if( p_box->i_type == ATOM_drmi )
1823 {
1824 msg_Warn( p_stream, "DRM protected streams are not supported." );
1825 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
1826 }
1827
1828 MP4_ReadBoxContainerRaw( p_stream, p_box );
1829
1830#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1831 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"vide\" in stsd %dx%d depth %d",
1832 p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_width,
1833 p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_height,
1834 p_box->data.p_sample_vide->i_depth );
1835
1836#endif
1837 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
1838}

1853static int MP4_ReadBox_sample_text( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
1854{
1855 int32_t t;
1856
1857 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_sample_text_t );
1858
1859 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_reserved1 );
1860 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_reserved2 );
1861
1862 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_data_reference_index );
1863
1864 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_display_flags );
1865
1866 MP4_GET4BYTES( t );
1867 switch( t )
1868 {
1869 /* FIXME search right signification */
1870 case 1: // Center
1871 p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_justification_horizontal = 1;
1872 p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_justification_vertical = 1;
1873 break;
1874 case -1: // Flush Right
1875 p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_justification_horizontal = -1;
1876 p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_justification_vertical = -1;
1877 break;
1878 case -2: // Flush Left
1879 p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_justification_horizontal = 0;
1880 p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_justification_vertical = 0;
1881 break;
1882 case 0: // Flush Default
1883 default:
1884 p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_justification_horizontal = 1;
1885 p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_justification_vertical = -1;
1886 break;
1887 }
1888
1889 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_background_color[0] );
1890 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_background_color[1] );
1891 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_background_color[2] );
1892 p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_background_color[3] = 0xFF;
1893
1894 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_text_box_top );
1895 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_text_box_left );
1896 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_text_box_bottom );
1897 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_sample_text->i_text_box_right );
1898
1899#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
1900 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"text\" in stsd text" );
1901#endif
1902 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
1903}

2101static int MP4_ReadBox_stss( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
2102{
2103 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_stss_t );
2104
2105 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_stss );
2106
2107 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_stss->i_entry_count );
2108
2109 p_box->data.p_stss->i_sample_number =
2110 calloc( p_box->data.p_stss->i_entry_count, sizeof(uint32_t) );
2111 if( unlikely( p_box->data.p_stss->i_sample_number == NULL ) )
2112 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
2113
2114 unsigned int i;
2115 for( i = 0; (i < p_box->data.p_stss->i_entry_count )&&( i_read >= 4 ); i++ )
2116 {
2117
2118 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_stss->i_sample_number[i] );
2119 /* XXX in libmp4 sample begin at 0 */
2120 p_box->data.p_stss->i_sample_number[i]--;
2121 }
2122 if ( i < p_box->data.p_stss->i_entry_count )
2123 p_box->data.p_stss->i_entry_count = i;
2124
2125#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE

2219static int MP4_ReadBox_padb( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
2220{
2221 uint32_t count;
2222
2223 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_padb_t );
2224
2225 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_padb );
2226
2227 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_padb->i_sample_count );
2228 count = (p_box->data.p_padb->i_sample_count + 1) / 2;
2229
2230 p_box->data.p_padb->i_reserved1 = calloc( count, sizeof(uint16_t) );
2231 p_box->data.p_padb->i_pad2 = calloc( count, sizeof(uint16_t) );
2232 p_box->data.p_padb->i_reserved2 = calloc( count, sizeof(uint16_t) );
2233 p_box->data.p_padb->i_pad1 = calloc( count, sizeof(uint16_t) );
2234 if( p_box->data.p_padb->i_reserved1 == NULL
2235 || p_box->data.p_padb->i_pad2 == NULL
2236 || p_box->data.p_padb->i_reserved2 == NULL
2237 || p_box->data.p_padb->i_pad1 == NULL )
2238 {
2239 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
2240 }
2241
2242 for( unsigned int i = 0; i < i_read / 2 ; i++ )
2243 {
2244 if( i >= count )
2245 {
2246 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
2247 }
2248 p_box->data.p_padb->i_reserved1[i] = ( (*p_peek) >> 7 )&0x01;
2249 p_box->data.p_padb->i_pad2[i] = ( (*p_peek) >> 4 )&0x07;
2250 p_box->data.p_padb->i_reserved1[i] = ( (*p_peek) >> 3 )&0x01;
2251 p_box->data.p_padb->i_pad1[i] = ( (*p_peek) )&0x07;
2252
2253 p_peek += 1; i_read -= 1;
2254 }
2255
2256#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
2257 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"stdp\" entry-count %"PRId64,
2258 i_read / 2 );
2259
2260#endif
2261 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
2262}

2272static int MP4_ReadBox_elst( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
2273{
2274 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_elst_t );
2275
2276 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_elst );
2277
2278
2279 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_elst->i_entry_count );
2280
2281 p_box->data.p_elst->i_segment_duration =
2282 calloc( p_box->data.p_elst->i_entry_count, sizeof(uint64_t) );
2283 p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_time =
2284 calloc( p_box->data.p_elst->i_entry_count, sizeof(int64_t) );
2285 p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_rate_integer =
2286 calloc( p_box->data.p_elst->i_entry_count, sizeof(uint16_t) );
2287 p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_rate_fraction =
2288 calloc( p_box->data.p_elst->i_entry_count, sizeof(uint16_t) );
2289 if( p_box->data.p_elst->i_segment_duration == NULL
2290 || p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_time == NULL
2291 || p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_rate_integer == NULL
2292 || p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_rate_fraction == NULL )
2293 {
2294 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
2295 }
2296
2297 unsigned i;
2298 for( i = 0; i < p_box->data.p_elst->i_entry_count; i++ )
2299 {
2300 if( p_box->data.p_elst->i_version == 1 )
2301 {
2302 if ( i_read < 20 )
2303 break;
2304 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_elst->i_segment_duration[i] );
2305
2306 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_time[i] );
2307 }
2308 else
2309 {
2310 if ( i_read < 12 )
2311 break;
2312 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_elst->i_segment_duration[i] );
2313
2314 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_time[i] );
2315 p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_time[i] = (int32_t)p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_time[i];
2316 }
2317
2318 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_rate_integer[i] );
2319 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_box->data.p_elst->i_media_rate_fraction[i] );
2320 }
2321 if ( i < p_box->data.p_elst->i_entry_count )
2322 p_box->data.p_elst->i_entry_count = i;
2323#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
2324 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"elst\" entry-count %lu",
2325 (unsigned long)p_box->data.p_elst->i_entry_count );
2326#endif
2327 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
2328}

2405
2406static int MP4_ReadBox_cmov( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
2407{
2408 MP4_Box_t *p_dcom;
2409 MP4_Box_t *p_cmvd;
2410
2411#ifdef HAVE_ZLIB_H
2412 stream_t *p_stream_memory;
2413 z_stream z_data;
2414 uint8_t *p_data;
2415 int i_result;
2416#endif
2417
2418 if( !( p_box->data.p_cmov = calloc(1, sizeof( MP4_Box_data_cmov_t ) ) ) )
2419 return 0;
2420
2421 if( !p_box->p_father ||
2422 ( p_box->p_father->i_type != ATOM_moov &&
2423 p_box->p_father->i_type != ATOM_foov ) )
2424 {
2425 msg_Warn( p_stream, "Read box: \"cmov\" box alone" );
2426 return 1;
2427 }
2428
2429 if( !MP4_ReadBoxContainer( p_stream, p_box ) )
2430 {
2431 return 0;
2432 }
2433
2434 if( ( p_dcom = MP4_BoxGet( p_box, "dcom" ) ) == NULL ||
2435 ( p_cmvd = MP4_BoxGet( p_box, "cmvd" ) ) == NULL ||
2436 p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->p_data == NULL )
2437 {
2438 msg_Warn( p_stream, "read box: \"cmov\" incomplete" );
2439 return 0;
2440 }
2441
2442 if( p_dcom->data.p_dcom->i_algorithm != ATOM_zlib )
2443 {
2444 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"cmov\" compression algorithm : %4.4s "
2445 "not supported", (char*)&p_dcom->data.p_dcom->i_algorithm );
2446 return 0;
2447 }
2448
2449#ifndef HAVE_ZLIB_H
2450 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"cmov\" zlib unsupported" );
2451 return 0;
2452
2453#else
2454 /* decompress data */
2455 /* allocate a new buffer */
2456 if( !( p_data = malloc( p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->i_uncompressed_size ) ) )
2457 return 0;
2458 /* init default structures */
2459 z_data.next_in = p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->p_data;
2460 z_data.avail_in = p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->i_compressed_size;
2461 z_data.next_out = p_data;
2462 z_data.avail_out = p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->i_uncompressed_size;
2463 z_data.zalloc = (alloc_func)Z_NULL;
2464 z_data.zfree = (free_func)Z_NULL;
2465 z_data.opaque = (voidpf)Z_NULL;
2466
2467 /* init zlib */
2468 if( inflateInit( &z_data ) != Z_OK )
2469 {
2470 msg_Err( p_stream, "read box: \"cmov\" error while uncompressing" );
2471 free( p_data );
2472 return 0;
2473 }
2474
2475 /* uncompress */
2476 i_result = inflate( &z_data, Z_NO_FLUSH );
2477 if( i_result != Z_OK && i_result != Z_STREAM_END )
2478 {
2479 msg_Err( p_stream, "read box: \"cmov\" error while uncompressing" );
2480 free( p_data );
2481 return 0;
2482 }
2483
2484 if( p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->i_uncompressed_size != z_data.total_out )
2485 {
2486 msg_Warn( p_stream, "read box: \"cmov\" uncompressing data size "
2487 "mismatch" );
2488 }
2489 p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->i_uncompressed_size = z_data.total_out;
2490
2491 /* close zlib */
2492 if( inflateEnd( &z_data ) != Z_OK )
2493 {
2494 msg_Warn( p_stream, "read box: \"cmov\" error while uncompressing "
2495 "data (ignored)" );
2496 }
2497
2498 free( p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->p_data );
2499 p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->p_data = p_data;
2500 p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->b_compressed = 0;
2501
2502 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"cmov\" box successfully uncompressed" );
2503
2504 /* now create a memory stream */
2505 p_stream_memory =
2506 stream_MemoryNew( VLC_OBJECT(p_stream), p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->p_data,
2507 p_cmvd->data.p_cmvd->i_uncompressed_size, true );
2508
2509 /* and read uncompressd moov */
2510 p_box->data.p_cmov->p_moov = MP4_ReadBox( p_stream_memory, NULL );
2511
2512 stream_Delete( p_stream_memory );
2513
2514#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
2515 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"cmov\" compressed movie header completed");
2516#endif
2517
2518 return p_box->data.p_cmov->p_moov ? 1 : 0;
2519#endif /* HAVE_ZLIB_H */
2520}

2669#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
2670 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"name\" text=`%s'",
2671 p_box->data.p_name->psz_text );
2672#endif
2673 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
2674}

2704static int MP4_ReadBox_0xa9xxx( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
2705{
2706 uint16_t i16;
2707
2708 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_0xa9xxx_t );
2709
2710 p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text = NULL;
2711
2712 MP4_GET2BYTES( i16 );
2713
2714 if( i16 > 0 )
2715 {
2716 int i_length = i16;
2717
2718 MP4_GET2BYTES( i16 );
2719 if( i_length >= i_read ) i_length = i_read + 1;
2720
2721 p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text = malloc( i_length );
2722 if( p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text == NULL )
2723 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
2724
2725 i_length--;
2726 memcpy( p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text,
2727 p_peek, i_length );
2728 p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text[i_length] = '\0';
2729
2730#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
2731 msg_Dbg( p_stream,
2732 "read box: \"c%3.3s\" text=`%s'",
2733 ((char*)&p_box->i_type + 1),
2734 p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text );
2735#endif
2736 }
2737 else
2738 {
2739 /* try iTune/Quicktime format, rewind to start */
2740 p_peek -= 2; i_read += 2;
2741 // we are expecting a 'data' box
2742 uint32_t i_data_len;
2743 uint32_t i_data_tag;
2744
2745 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_data_len );
2746 if( i_data_len > i_read ) i_data_len = i_read;
2747 MP4_GETFOURCC( i_data_tag );
2748 if( (i_data_len > 0) && (i_data_tag == ATOM_data) )
2749 {
2750 /* data box contains a version/flags field */
2751 uint32_t i_version;
2752 uint32_t i_reserved;
2753 VLC_UNUSED(i_reserved);
2754 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_version );
2755 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_reserved );
2756 // version should be 0, flags should be 1 for text, 0 for data
2757 if( ( i_version == 0x00000001 ) && (i_data_len >= 12 ) )
2758 {
2759 // the rest is the text
2760 i_data_len -= 12;
2761 p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text = malloc( i_data_len + 1 );
2762 if( p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text == NULL )
2763 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
2764
2765 memcpy( p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text,
2766 p_peek, i_data_len );
2767 p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text[i_data_len] = '\0';
2768#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
2769 msg_Dbg( p_stream,
2770 "read box: \"c%3.3s\" text=`%s'",
2771 ((char*)&p_box->i_type+1),
2772 p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text );
2773#endif
2774 }
2775 else
2776 {
2777 // TODO: handle data values for ID3 tag values, track num or cover art,etc...
2778 }
2779 }
2780 }
2781
2782 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
2783}
2784static void MP4_FreeBox_0xa9xxx( MP4_Box_t *p_box )
2785{
2786 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_0xa9xxx->psz_text );
2787}

2797static int MP4_ReadBox_chpl( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
2798{
2799 MP4_Box_data_chpl_t *p_chpl;
2800 uint32_t i_dummy;
2801 VLC_UNUSED(i_dummy);
2802 int i;
2803 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_chpl_t );
2804
2805 p_chpl = p_box->data.p_chpl;
2806
2807 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_chpl );
2808
2809 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_dummy );
2810
2811 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_chpl->i_chapter );
2812
2813 for( i = 0; i < p_chpl->i_chapter; i++ )
2814 {
2815 uint64_t i_start;
2816 uint8_t i_len;
2817 int i_copy;
2818 MP4_GET8BYTES( i_start );
2819 MP4_GET1BYTE( i_len );
2820
2821 p_chpl->chapter[i].psz_name = malloc( i_len + 1 );
2822 if( !p_chpl->chapter[i].psz_name )
2823 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
2824
2825 i_copy = __MIN( i_len, i_read );
2826 if( i_copy > 0 )
2827 memcpy( p_chpl->chapter[i].psz_name, p_peek, i_copy );
2828 p_chpl->chapter[i].psz_name[i_copy] = '\0';
2829 p_chpl->chapter[i].i_start = i_start;
2830
2831 p_peek += i_copy;
2832 i_read -= i_copy;
2833 }
2834 /* Bubble sort by increasing start date */
2835 do
2836 {
2837 for( i = 0; i < p_chpl->i_chapter - 1; i++ )
2838 {
2839 if( p_chpl->chapter[i].i_start > p_chpl->chapter[i+1].i_start )
2840 {
2841 char *psz = p_chpl->chapter[i+1].psz_name;
2842 int64_t i64 = p_chpl->chapter[i+1].i_start;
2843
2844 p_chpl->chapter[i+1].psz_name = p_chpl->chapter[i].psz_name;
2845 p_chpl->chapter[i+1].i_start = p_chpl->chapter[i].i_start;
2846
2847 p_chpl->chapter[i].psz_name = psz;
2848 p_chpl->chapter[i].i_start = i64;
2849
2850 i = -1;
2851 break;
2852 }
2853 }
2854 } while( i == -1 );
2855
2856#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
2857 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "read box: \"chpl\" %d chapters",
2858 p_chpl->i_chapter );
2859#endif
2860 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
2861}

2890static int MP4_ReadBox_meta( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
2891{
2892 uint8_t meta_data[8];
2893 int i_actually_read;
2894
2895 // skip over box header
2896 i_actually_read = stream_Read( p_stream, meta_data, 8 );
2897 if( i_actually_read < 8 )
2898 return 0;
2899
2900 if ( !p_box->p_father )
2901 return 0;
2902
2903 switch( p_box->p_father->i_type )
2904 {
2905 case ATOM_udta: /* itunes udta/meta */
2906 /* meta content starts with a 4 byte version/flags value (should be 0) */
2907 i_actually_read = stream_Read( p_stream, meta_data, 4 );
2908 if( i_actually_read < 4 )
2909 return 0;
2910
2911 /* then it behaves like a container */
2912 return MP4_ReadBoxContainerRaw( p_stream, p_box );
2913
2914 default: /* regular meta atom */
2915
2916 i_actually_read = stream_Read( p_stream, meta_data, 8 );
2917 if( i_actually_read < 8 )
2918 return 0;
2919
2920 /* Mandatory */
2921 if ( VLC_FOURCC( meta_data[4], meta_data[5], meta_data[6], meta_data[7] ) != ATOM_hdlr )
2922 return 0;
2923
2924 //ft
2925 }
2926 return 1;
2927}

3069static int MP4_ReadBox_tfra( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
3070{
3071 uint32_t i_number_of_entries;
3072 MP4_READBOX_ENTER( MP4_Box_data_tfra_t );
3073 MP4_Box_data_tfra_t *p_tfra = p_box->data.p_tfra;
3074 MP4_GETVERSIONFLAGS( p_box->data.p_tfra );
3075
3076 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_tfra->i_track_ID );
3077 uint32_t i_lengths = 0;
3078 MP4_GET4BYTES( i_lengths );
3079 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_tfra->i_number_of_entries );
3080 i_number_of_entries = p_tfra->i_number_of_entries;
3081 p_tfra->i_length_size_of_traf_num = i_lengths >> 4;
3082 p_tfra->i_length_size_of_trun_num = ( i_lengths & 0x0c ) >> 2;
3083 p_tfra->i_length_size_of_sample_num = i_lengths & 0x03;
3084
3085 size_t size = 4 + 4*p_tfra->i_version; /* size in {4, 8} */
3086 p_tfra->p_time = calloc( i_number_of_entries, size );
3087 p_tfra->p_moof_offset = calloc( i_number_of_entries, size );
3088
3089 size = 1 + p_tfra->i_length_size_of_traf_num; /* size in [|1, 4|] */
3090 p_tfra->p_traf_number = calloc( i_number_of_entries, size );
3091 size = 1 + p_tfra->i_length_size_of_trun_num;
3092 p_tfra->p_trun_number = calloc( i_number_of_entries, size );
3093 size = 1 + p_tfra->i_length_size_of_sample_num;
3094 p_tfra->p_sample_number = calloc( i_number_of_entries, size );
3095
3096 if( !p_tfra->p_time || !p_tfra->p_moof_offset || !p_tfra->p_traf_number
3097 || !p_tfra->p_trun_number || !p_tfra->p_sample_number )
3098 goto error;
3099
3100 int i_fields_length = 3 + p_tfra->i_length_size_of_traf_num
3101 + p_tfra->i_length_size_of_trun_num
3102 + p_tfra->i_length_size_of_sample_num;
3103
3104 uint32_t i;
3105 for( i = 0; i < i_number_of_entries; i++ )
3106 {
3107
3108 if( p_tfra->i_version == 1 )
3109 {
3110 if ( i_read < i_fields_length + 16 )
3111 break;
3112 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_tfra->p_time[i*2] );
3113 MP4_GET8BYTES( p_tfra->p_moof_offset[i*2] );
3114 }
3115 else
3116 {
3117 if ( i_read < i_fields_length + 8 )
3118 break;
3119 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_tfra->p_time[i] );
3120 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_tfra->p_moof_offset[i] );
3121 }
3122 switch (p_tfra->i_length_size_of_traf_num)
3123 {
3124 case 0:
3125 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_tfra->p_traf_number[i] );
3126 break;
3127 case 1:
3128 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_tfra->p_traf_number[i*2] );
3129 break;
3130 case 2:
3131 MP4_GET3BYTES( p_tfra->p_traf_number[i*3] );
3132 break;
3133 case 3:
3134 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_tfra->p_traf_number[i*4] );
3135 break;
3136 default:
3137 goto error;
3138 }
3139
3140 switch (p_tfra->i_length_size_of_trun_num)
3141 {
3142 case 0:
3143 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_tfra->p_trun_number[i] );
3144 break;
3145 case 1:
3146 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_tfra->p_trun_number[i*2] );
3147 break;
3148 case 2:
3149 MP4_GET3BYTES( p_tfra->p_trun_number[i*3] );
3150 break;
3151 case 3:
3152 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_tfra->p_trun_number[i*4] );
3153 break;
3154 default:
3155 goto error;
3156 }
3157
3158 switch (p_tfra->i_length_size_of_sample_num)
3159 {
3160 case 0:
3161 MP4_GET1BYTE( p_tfra->p_sample_number[i] );
3162 break;
3163 case 1:
3164 MP4_GET2BYTES( p_tfra->p_sample_number[i*2] );
3165 break;
3166 case 2:
3167 MP4_GET3BYTES( p_tfra->p_sample_number[i*3] );
3168 break;
3169 case 3:
3170 MP4_GET4BYTES( p_tfra->p_sample_number[i*4] );
3171 break;
3172 default:
3173 goto error;
3174 }
3175 }
3176 if ( i < i_number_of_entries )
3177 i_number_of_entries = i;
3178
3179#ifdef MP4_VERBOSE
3180 if( p_tfra->i_version == 0 )
3181 {
3182 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "time[0]: %"PRIu32", moof_offset[0]: %"PRIx32"",
3183 p_tfra->p_time[0], p_tfra->p_moof_offset[0] );
3184
3185 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "time[1]: %"PRIu32", moof_offset[1]: %"PRIx32"",
3186 p_tfra->p_time[1], p_tfra->p_moof_offset[1] );
3187 }
3188 else
3189 {
3190 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "time[0]: %"PRIu64", moof_offset[0]: %"PRIx64"",
3191 ((uint64_t *)(p_tfra->p_time))[0],
3192 ((uint64_t *)(p_tfra->p_moof_offset))[0] );
3193
3194 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "time[1]: %"PRIu64", moof_offset[1]: %"PRIx64"",
3195 ((uint64_t *)(p_tfra->p_time))[1],
3196 ((uint64_t *)(p_tfra->p_moof_offset))[1] );
3197 }
3198
3199 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "number_of_entries is %"PRIu32"", i_number_of_entries );
3200 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "track ID is: %"PRIu32"", p_tfra->i_track_ID );
3201#endif
3202
3203 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 1 );
3204error:
3205 MP4_READBOX_EXIT( 0 );
3206}

3208static void MP4_FreeBox_tfra( MP4_Box_t *p_box )
3209{
3210 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_tfra->p_time );
3211 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_tfra->p_moof_offset );
3212 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_tfra->p_traf_number );
3213 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_tfra->p_trun_number );
3214 FREENULL( p_box->data.p_tfra->p_sample_number );
3215}

3218/* For generic */
3219static int MP4_ReadBox_default( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
3220{
3221 if( !p_box->p_father )
3222 {
3223 goto unknown;
3224 }
3225 if( p_box->p_father->i_type == ATOM_stsd )
3226 {
3227 MP4_Box_t *p_mdia = MP4_BoxGet( p_box, "../../../.." );
3228 MP4_Box_t *p_hdlr;
3229
3230 if( p_mdia == NULL || p_mdia->i_type != ATOM_mdia ||
3231 (p_hdlr = MP4_BoxGet( p_mdia, "hdlr" )) == NULL )
3232 {
3233 goto unknown;
3234 }
3235 switch( p_hdlr->data.p_hdlr->i_handler_type )
3236 {
3237 case ATOM_soun:
3238 return MP4_ReadBox_sample_soun( p_stream, p_box );
3239 case ATOM_vide:
3240 return MP4_ReadBox_sample_vide( p_stream, p_box );
3241 case ATOM_text:
3242 return MP4_ReadBox_sample_text( p_stream, p_box );
3243 case ATOM_tx3g:
3244 case ATOM_sbtl:
3245 return MP4_ReadBox_sample_tx3g( p_stream, p_box );
3246 default:
3247 msg_Warn( p_stream,
3248 "unknown handler type in stsd (incompletely loaded)" );
3249 return 1;
3250 }
3251 }
3252
3253unknown:
3254 if MP4_BOX_TYPE_ASCII()
3255 msg_Warn( p_stream,
3256 "unknown box type %4.4s (incompletely loaded)",
3257 (char*)&p_box->i_type );
3258 else
3259 msg_Warn( p_stream,
3260 "unknown box type c%3.3s (incompletely loaded)",
3261 (char*)&p_box->i_type+1 );
3262
3263 return 1;
3264}

3525/*****************************************************************************
3526 * MP4_ReadBox : parse the actual box and the children
3527 * XXX : Do not go to the next box
3528 *****************************************************************************/
3529static MP4_Box_t *MP4_ReadBox( stream_t *p_stream, MP4_Box_t *p_father )
3530{
3531 MP4_Box_t *p_box = calloc( 1, sizeof( MP4_Box_t ) ); /* Needed to ensure simple on error handler */
3532 unsigned int i_index;
3533
3534 if( p_box == NULL )
3535 return NULL;
3536
3537 if( !MP4_ReadBoxCommon( p_stream, p_box ) )
3538 {
3539 msg_Warn( p_stream, "cannot read one box" );
3540 free( p_box );
3541 return NULL;
3542 }
3543 if( !p_box->i_size )
3544 {
3545 msg_Dbg( p_stream, "found an empty box (null size)" );
3546 free( p_box );
3547 return NULL;
3548 }
3549 p_box->p_father = p_father;
3550
3551 /* Now search function to call */
3552 for( i_index = 0; ; i_index++ )
3553 {
3554 if ( MP4_Box_Function[i_index].i_parent &&
3555 p_box->p_father &&
3556 p_box->p_father->i_type != MP4_Box_Function[i_index].i_parent )
3557 continue;
3558
3559 if( ( MP4_Box_Function[i_index].i_type == p_box->i_type )||
3560 ( MP4_Box_Function[i_index].i_type == 0 ) )
3561 {
3562 break;
3563 }
3564 }
3565
3566 if( !(MP4_Box_Function[i_index].MP4_ReadBox_function)( p_stream, p_box ) )
3567 {
3568 MP4_BoxFree( p_stream, p_box );
3569 return NULL;
3570 }
3571
3572 return p_box;
3573}
3574
3575/*****************************************************************************
3576 * MP4_FreeBox : free memory after read with MP4_ReadBox and all
3577 * the children
3578 *****************************************************************************/
3579void MP4_BoxFree( stream_t *s, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
3580{
3581 unsigned int i_index;
3582 MP4_Box_t *p_child;
3583
3584 if( !p_box )
3585 return; /* hehe */
3586
3587 for( p_child = p_box->p_first; p_child != NULL; )
3588 {
3589 MP4_Box_t *p_next;
3590
3591 p_next = p_child->p_next;
3592 MP4_BoxFree( s, p_child );
3593 p_child = p_next;
3594 }
3595
3596 /* Now search function to call */
3597 if( p_box->data.p_payload )
3598 {
3599 for( i_index = 0; ; i_index++ )
3600 {
3601 if( ( MP4_Box_Function[i_index].i_type == p_box->i_type )||
3602 ( MP4_Box_Function[i_index].i_type == 0 ) )
3603 {
3604 break;
3605 }
3606 }
3607 if( MP4_Box_Function[i_index].MP4_FreeBox_function == NULL )
3608 {
3609 /* Should not happen */
3610 if MP4_BOX_TYPE_ASCII()
3611 msg_Warn( s,
3612 "cannot free box %4.4s, type unknown",
3613 (char*)&p_box->i_type );
3614 else
3615 msg_Warn( s,
3616 "cannot free box c%3.3s, type unknown",
3617 (char*)&p_box->i_type+1 );
3618 }
3619 else
3620 {
3621 MP4_Box_Function[i_index].MP4_FreeBox_function( p_box );
3622 }
3623 free( p_box->data.p_payload );
3624 }
3625 free( p_box );
3626}

3628/* SmooBox is a very simple MP4 box, VLC specific, used only for the stream_filter to
3629 * send information to the demux. SmooBox is actually a simplified moov box (we wanted
3630 * to avoid the hassle of building a moov box at the stream_filter level) */
3631MP4_Box_t *MP4_BoxGetSmooBox( stream_t *s )
3632{
3633 /* p_chunk is a virtual root container for the smoo box */
3634 MP4_Box_t *p_chunk;
3635 MP4_Box_t *p_smoo;
3636
3637 p_chunk = calloc( 1, sizeof( MP4_Box_t ) );
3638 if( unlikely( p_chunk == NULL ) )
3639 return NULL;
3640
3641 p_chunk->i_type = ATOM_root;
3642 p_chunk->i_shortsize = 1;
3643
3644 p_smoo = MP4_ReadBox( s, p_chunk );
3645 if( !p_smoo || p_smoo->i_type != ATOM_uuid || CmpUUID( &p_smoo->i_uuid, &SmooBoxUUID ) )
3646 {
3647 msg_Warn( s, "no smoo box found!");
3648 goto error;
3649 }
3650
3651 p_chunk->p_first = p_smoo;
3652 p_chunk->p_last = p_smoo;
3653
3654 return p_chunk;
3655
3656error:
3657 free( p_chunk );
3658 return NULL;
3659}

3661MP4_Box_t *MP4_BoxGetNextChunk( stream_t *s )
3662{
3663 /* p_chunk is a virtual root container for the moof and mdat boxes */
3664 MP4_Box_t *p_chunk;
3665 MP4_Box_t *p_tmp_box = NULL;
3666
3667 p_tmp_box = calloc( 1, sizeof( MP4_Box_t ) );
3668 if( unlikely( p_tmp_box == NULL ) )
3669 return NULL;
3670
3671 /* We might get a ftyp box or a SmooBox */
3672 MP4_ReadBoxCommon( s, p_tmp_box );
3673
3674 if( (p_tmp_box->i_type == ATOM_uuid && !CmpUUID( &p_tmp_box->i_uuid, &SmooBoxUUID )) )
3675 {
3676 free( p_tmp_box );
3677 return MP4_BoxGetSmooBox( s );
3678 }
3679 else if( p_tmp_box->i_type == ATOM_ftyp )
3680 {
3681 free( p_tmp_box );
3682 return MP4_BoxGetRoot( s );
3683 }
3684 free( p_tmp_box );
3685
3686 p_chunk = calloc( 1, sizeof( MP4_Box_t ) );
3687 if( unlikely( p_chunk == NULL ) )
3688 return NULL;
3689
3690 p_chunk->i_type = ATOM_root;
3691 p_chunk->i_shortsize = 1;
3692
3693 MP4_ReadBoxContainerChildren( s, p_chunk, ATOM_moof );
3694
3695 p_tmp_box = p_chunk->p_first;
3696 while( p_tmp_box )
3697 {
3698 p_chunk->i_size += p_tmp_box->i_size;
3699 p_tmp_box = p_tmp_box->p_next;
3700 }
3701
3702 return p_chunk;
3703}

3705/*****************************************************************************
3706 * MP4_BoxGetRoot : Parse the entire file, and create all boxes in memory
3707 *****************************************************************************
3708 * The first box is a virtual box "root" and is the father for all first
3709 * level boxes for the file, a sort of virtual contener
3710 *****************************************************************************/
3711MP4_Box_t *MP4_BoxGetRoot( stream_t *s )
3712{
3713 MP4_Box_t *p_root;
3714 stream_t *p_stream;
3715 int i_result;
3716
3717 p_root = malloc( sizeof( MP4_Box_t ) );
3718 if( p_root == NULL )
3719 return NULL;
3720
3721 p_root->i_pos = 0;
3722 p_root->i_type = ATOM_root;
3723 p_root->i_shortsize = 1;
3724 /* could be a DASH stream for exemple, 0 means unknown or infinite size */
3725 p_root->i_size = 0;
3726 CreateUUID( &p_root->i_uuid, p_root->i_type );
3727
3728 p_root->data.p_payload = NULL;
3729 p_root->p_father = NULL;
3730 p_root->p_first = NULL;
3731 p_root->p_last = NULL;
3732 p_root->p_next = NULL;
3733
3734 p_stream = s;
3735
3736 /* First get the moov */
3737 i_result = MP4_ReadBoxContainerChildren( p_stream, p_root, ATOM_moov );
3738
3739 if( !i_result )
3740 goto error;
3741 /* If there is a mvex box, it means fragmented MP4, and we're done */
3742 else if( MP4_BoxCount( p_root, "moov/mvex" ) > 0 )
3743 return p_root;
3744
3745 p_root->i_size = stream_Size( s );
3746 if( stream_Tell( s ) + 8 < stream_Size( s ) )
3747 {
3748 /* Get the rest of the file */
3749 i_result = MP4_ReadBoxContainerRaw( p_stream, p_root );
3750
3751 if( !i_result )
3752 goto error;
3753 }
3754
3755 MP4_Box_t *p_moov;
3756 MP4_Box_t *p_cmov;
3757
3758 /* check if there is a cmov, if so replace
3759 compressed moov by uncompressed one */
3760 if( ( ( p_moov = MP4_BoxGet( p_root, "moov" ) ) &&
3761 ( p_cmov = MP4_BoxGet( p_root, "moov/cmov" ) ) ) ||
3762 ( ( p_moov = MP4_BoxGet( p_root, "foov" ) ) &&
3763 ( p_cmov = MP4_BoxGet( p_root, "foov/cmov" ) ) ) )
3764 {
3765 /* rename the compressed moov as a box to skip */
3766 p_moov->i_type = ATOM_skip;
3767
3768 /* get uncompressed p_moov */
3769 p_moov = p_cmov->data.p_cmov->p_moov;
3770 p_cmov->data.p_cmov->p_moov = NULL;
3771
3772 /* make p_root father of this new moov */
3773 p_moov->p_father = p_root;
3774
3775 /* insert this new moov box as first child of p_root */
3776 p_moov->p_next = p_root->p_first;
3777 p_root->p_first = p_moov;
3778 }
3779
3780 return p_root;
3781
3782error:
3783 free( p_root );
3784 stream_Seek( p_stream, 0 );
3785 return NULL;
3786}

3789static void MP4_BoxDumpStructure_Internal( stream_t *s,
3790 MP4_Box_t *p_box, unsigned int i_level )
3791{
3792 MP4_Box_t *p_child;
3793
3794 if( !i_level )
3795 {
3796 if MP4_BOX_TYPE_ASCII()
3797 msg_Dbg( s, "dumping root Box \"%4.4s\"",
3798 (char*)&p_box->i_type );
3799 else
3800 msg_Dbg( s, "dumping root Box \"c%3.3s\"",
3801 (char*)&p_box->i_type+1 );
3802 }
3803 else
3804 {
3805 char str[512];
3806 if( i_level >= (sizeof(str) - 1)/4 )
3807 return;
3808
3809 memset( str, ' ', sizeof(str) );
3810 for( unsigned i = 0; i < i_level; i++ )
3811 {
3812 str[i*4] = '|';
3813 }
3814 if( MP4_BOX_TYPE_ASCII() )
3815 snprintf( &str[i_level * 4], sizeof(str) - 4*i_level,
3816 "+ %4.4s size %"PRIu64" offset %ld",
3817 (char*)&p_box->i_type, p_box->i_size, p_box->i_pos );
3818 else
3819 snprintf( &str[i_level * 4], sizeof(str) - 4*i_level,
3820 "+ c%3.3s size %"PRIu64" offset %ld",
3821 (char*)&p_box->i_type+1, p_box->i_size, p_box->i_pos );
3822 msg_Dbg( s, "%s", str );
3823 }
3824 p_child = p_box->p_first;
3825 while( p_child )
3826 {
3827 MP4_BoxDumpStructure_Internal( s, p_child, i_level + 1 );
3828 p_child = p_child->p_next;
3829 }
3830}
3831
3832void MP4_BoxDumpStructure( stream_t *s, MP4_Box_t *p_box )
3833{
3834 MP4_BoxDumpStructure_Internal( s, p_box, 0 );
3835}

3838/*****************************************************************************
3839 *****************************************************************************
3840 **
3841 ** High level methods to acces an MP4 file
3842 **
3843 *****************************************************************************
3844 *****************************************************************************/
3845static void get_token( char **ppsz_path, char **ppsz_token, int *pi_number )
3846{
3847 size_t i_len ;
3848 if( !*ppsz_path[0] )
3849 {
3850 *ppsz_token = NULL;
3851 *pi_number = 0;
3852 return;
3853 }
3854 i_len = strcspn( *ppsz_path, "/[" );
3855 if( !i_len && **ppsz_path == '/' )
3856 {
3857 i_len = 1;
3858 }
3859 *ppsz_token = strndup( *ppsz_path, i_len );
3860 if( unlikely(!*ppsz_token) )
3861 abort();
3862
3863 *ppsz_path += i_len;
3864
3865 if( **ppsz_path == '[' )
3866 {
3867 (*ppsz_path)++;
3868 *pi_number = strtol( *ppsz_path, NULL, 10 );
3869 while( **ppsz_path && **ppsz_path != ']' )
3870 {
3871 (*ppsz_path)++;
3872 }
3873 if( **ppsz_path == ']' )
3874 {
3875 (*ppsz_path)++;
3876 }
3877 }
3878 else
3879 {
3880 *pi_number = 0;
3881 }
3882 while( **ppsz_path == '/' )
3883 {
3884 (*ppsz_path)++;
3885 }
3886}
