3888static void MP4_BoxGet_Internal( MP4_Box_t **pp_result,
3889 MP4_Box_t *p_box, const char *psz_fmt, va_list args)
3890{
3891 char *psz_dup;
3892 char *psz_path;
3893 char *psz_token;
3894
3895 if( !p_box )
3896 {
3897 *pp_result = NULL;
3898 return;
3899 }
3900
3901 if( vasprintf( &psz_path, psz_fmt, args ) == -1 )
3902 psz_path = NULL;
3903
3904 if( !psz_path || !psz_path[0] )
3905 {
3906 free( psz_path );
3907 *pp_result = NULL;
3908 return;
3909 }
3910
3911// fprintf( stderr, "path:'%s'\n", psz_path );
3912 psz_dup = psz_path; /* keep this pointer, as it need to be unallocated */
3913 for( ; ; )
3914 {
3915 int i_number;
3916
3917 get_token( &psz_path, &psz_token, &i_number );
3918// fprintf( stderr, "path:'%s', token:'%s' n:%d\n",
3919// psz_path,psz_token,i_number );
3920 if( !psz_token )
3921 {
3922 free( psz_dup );
3923 *pp_result = p_box;
3924 return;
3925 }
3926 else
3927 if( !strcmp( psz_token, "/" ) )
3928 {
3929 /* Find root box */
3930 while( p_box && p_box->i_type != ATOM_root )
3931 {
3932 p_box = p_box->p_father;
3933 }
3934 if( !p_box )
3935 {
3936 goto error_box;
3937 }
3938 }
3939 else
3940 if( !strcmp( psz_token, "." ) )
3941 {
3942 /* Do nothing */
3943 }
3944 else
3945 if( !strcmp( psz_token, ".." ) )
3946 {
3947 p_box = p_box->p_father;
3948 if( !p_box )
3949 {
3950 goto error_box;
3951 }
3952 }
3953 else
3954 if( strlen( psz_token ) == 4 )
3955 {
3956 uint32_t i_fourcc;
3957 i_fourcc = VLC_FOURCC( psz_token[0], psz_token[1],
3958 psz_token[2], psz_token[3] );
3959 p_box = p_box->p_first;
3960 for( ; ; )
3961 {
3962 if( !p_box )
3963 {
3964 goto error_box;
3965 }
3966 if( p_box->i_type == i_fourcc )
3967 {
3968 if( !i_number )
3969 {
3970 break;
3971 }
3972 i_number--;
3973 }
3974 p_box = p_box->p_next;
3975 }
3976 }
3977 else
3978 if( *psz_token == '\0' )
3979 {
3980 p_box = p_box->p_first;
3981 for( ; ; )
3982 {
3983 if( !p_box )
3984 {
3985 goto error_box;
3986 }
3987 if( !i_number )
3988 {
3989 break;
3990 }
3991 i_number--;
3992 p_box = p_box->p_next;
3993 }
3994 }
3995 else
3996 {
3997// fprintf( stderr, "Argg malformed token \"%s\"",psz_token );
3998 goto error_box;
3999 }
4000
4001 FREENULL( psz_token );
4002 }
4003
4004 return;
4005
4006error_box:
4007 free( psz_token );
4008 free( psz_dup );
4009 *pp_result = NULL;
4010 return;
4011}

4013/*****************************************************************************
4014 * MP4_BoxGet: find a box given a path relative to p_box
4015 *****************************************************************************
4016 * Path Format: . .. / as usual
4017 * [number] to specifie box number ex: trak[12]
4018 *
4019 * ex: /moov/trak[12]
4020 * ../mdia
4021 *****************************************************************************/
4022MP4_Box_t *MP4_BoxGet( MP4_Box_t *p_box, const char *psz_fmt, ... )
4023{
4024 va_list args;
4025 MP4_Box_t *p_result;
4026
4027 va_start( args, psz_fmt );
4028 MP4_BoxGet_Internal( &p_result, p_box, psz_fmt, args );
4029 va_end( args );
4030
4031 return( p_result );
4032}

4034/*****************************************************************************
4035 * MP4_BoxCount: count box given a path relative to p_box
4036 *****************************************************************************
4037 * Path Format: . .. / as usual
4038 * [number] to specifie box number ex: trak[12]
4039 *
4040 * ex: /moov/trak[12]
4041 * ../mdia
4042 *****************************************************************************/
4043int MP4_BoxCount( MP4_Box_t *p_box, const char *psz_fmt, ... )
4044{
4045 va_list args;
4046 int i_count;
4047 MP4_Box_t *p_result, *p_next;
4048
4049 va_start( args, psz_fmt );
4050 MP4_BoxGet_Internal( &p_result, p_box, psz_fmt, args );
4051 va_end( args );
4052 if( !p_result )
4053 {
4054 return( 0 );
4055 }
4056
4057 i_count = 1;
4058 for( p_next = p_result->p_next; p_next != NULL; p_next = p_next->p_next)
4059 {
4060 if( p_next->i_type == p_result->i_type)
4061 {
4062 i_count++;
4063 }
4064 }
4065 return( i_count );
4066}
